	<div id="intro">
	<h2>Introduction</h2>
	<p>This document describes the <a href="http://www.collada.org/2005/11/COLLADASchema">COLLADA 1.4 Schema</a> namespace. The specifications are designed and developed by the <a href="http://khronos.org/collada">COLLADA Work Group</a> of <a href="http://khronos.org">The Khronos Group</a>, a member funded consortium focused on the creation of open standard APIs for dynamic media. This document also contains a directory of links to these related resources, using <a href="http://www.rddl.org/">Resource Directory Description Language</a>.</p>
	</div>
